data.description: Single story home. With a bit of love this home could be better, Some remodeling done over 10 years ago. Small kitchen with family room. Hardwood floors 10 years old. Formal living room 1041 Living square feet. Built in pool in the back yard over 20 years old. Fire place not to code - oven in fireplace needs to be removed - county requirement Also fire inside the house by tenant 2015 - landlord is not reasonable Termites around outside of the house. All trees have been removed to help termite issue if possible
